<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 WIDTH=640 NOF=LY><TR VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><TD WIDTH=640><b><CENTER><FONT COLOR="#66FFCC" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica">Weekly Update.</FONT></b><FONT SIZE="-2" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica"><br>Thursday, January 24, 2002 by <a href="mailto:aerylin@shardsofavalon.com">Aerylin</a></FONT><br><br></CENTER><FONT SIZE="-1" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica"><center><br>Well, we've come and gone during the week, most notably clearing North-ToV today. Let's see what was served to us..<br><br><br>We Did Ssra Temple twice during the week, clearing out named and checking the zone. We were lucky enough to slay "somewierdnameorother The Exiled" for the first time on Xegony and one of the few servers to do it. He and his friends dropped a few nice things, had a deadly look mace..too bad the stats sucked and it was pal/sk only. ~Grats Rot on that one. Really nice Ranged Item for <b>Auen</b>, Whip for Bryden and other such goodies i've forgotten the names of.<br><br>We did ToV a few days ago, the zone promptly crashing after making good progress. Today we made even better progress and cleared our scaled friends flawlessly in record time.<br><br>Vulak gave <b>Evander</b> a nice new Crystal Ring, Aztek a Cord and Brody got a nice Nerf-Stick.<br><br>That's all folks! I'd post screenshots, but i'm too damned lazy this time.</FONT></TD></TR><BR><BR></TABLE>
<a name="newsitem1010810053,64146,"></a>
