<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 WIDTH=640 NOF=LY><TR VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><TD WIDTH=640><b><CENTER><FONT COLOR="#66FFCC" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica">Nwing dead... Twice.</FONT></b><FONT SIZE="-2" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica"><br>Thursday, October 11, 2001 by <a href="mailto:zammel@shardsofavalon.com">Zammel</a></FONT><br><br></CENTER><FONT SIZE="-1" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica">Well we're all too lazy to update the webpage regularly, so we've cleared North Wing TOV twice since the last update, thanks to the patch. We also did some ST raiding with IS on the server up, although we didnt manage to kill the 3rd warder, due to the fact we only had 20 people, we still got a few nice drops.<br><br>Noteable drops include two Windraiders Belt's, Mithril Helm, Orb of the Deep Sea, Nevederia's Horn, and other assorted goodies. The first Vulak dropped a Tolans Longsword of the Glade for Skanda (IS), Vyrinn's Earring of Insanity for <b>Flaen</b> and a now upgraded Palladius' Axe of the Slaughter, for <b>Sober</b>, who is also to be congratulated for breaking 1700 AC barrier today. <br><br>The patch saw a NToV respawn, which was promptly cleared again. Vulak recieved an upgrade, and gave us a bit of trouble at the start of the fight, especially because he came with two drake friends, but we managed to pull through and kill him on our first shot. He dropped his best load to date - A pair of Do'Vassir's Gauntlets of Might for <b>Brienaire</b>, Crystasia's Crystal Ring, which went to Endar (OOK OOK!) if memory serves, and a NICE upgraded Gharn's Rock of Smashing, which was awarded to IS.<br><br>In our epic crusade against the most ferocious of NWing Dragons, Lord Koi`Doken, aka f33sh, we employed a secret tactic. Today, i will share that tactic with you, so you may all bask in the overwhelming glory of f33sh. Use a ranger to tank. Only the ranger super powers can save you against the might of the f33sh. Skanda tanked Koi`Doken for the entire fight and survived. Sad.<br><br><br><center><br><A HREF="/news/skandatank.jpg"><IMG SRC="/news/skandatankthumb.jpg" alt="So sad" target=new border=0></a></center><br></FONT></TD></TR><BR><BR></TABLE>
