<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 WIDTH=640 NOF=LY><TR VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><TD WIDTH=640><b><CENTER><FONT COLOR="#66FFCC" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica">Sontalak, Derakor and a bit of Masonry</FONT></b><FONT SIZE="-2" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica"><br>Tuesday, July 17, 2001 by <a href="mailto:aedalare@shardsofavalon.com">Aedalare</a></FONT><br><br></CENTER><FONT SIZE="-1" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica">Well it all started out fine. We went to pay a visit on Sontalak and see if we could coerce him into handing over a key to Sleepers Tomb. Well after extended discourse discussions broke down, with niether side willing to return to the negotiating table we said Stuff it and figured it would just be easier to kill him.<br><br>This ladies and gentlemen will go down in history as one of the ugliest fights ever to be succesful. That pug faced freak was all over the place, managing to take down our clerics in short order then go to work on melee, all the while sitten is jumping up and down in his face desperately trying to get his attention. I guess that as with most of us he just doesnt find an assling that intimidating...<br><br>At any rate he died and dead is dead so who really cares in the end. Grats to <b>Citron</b> on a shiney new sleepers tomb key, dunno who got the heavy legs he dropped. The more I ponder it the more I think Verant designed Sontalak last and were just to lazy to bother adding anything of vague value to him.<br><br>Next up came Derakor. Basically he was a speed hump on the way to Statue. Fight lasted all of a minute before he keeled over and assumed the position. Grats to <b>Zammel</b> on your shinee new <b><a href=http://eq.gameznet.com/equipment/bootsofthevindicator.html>Boots of the Vindicator</a></b>.<br><br>With plenty of daylight remaining we moved on to the main course - Hello Statue of Rallos Zek. This was a first time for alot of us and I for one want to say ~DAMN this guy has alot of hp. Wasn't an exceptionally long fight though, I dont have exact logs but I'm pretty sure we only went through 3 tanks, so around 9-10 minutes? I'll try find out exact time. Grats to Megdalie(IS) on her new <b><a href=http://www.gameznet.com/eq/equipment/cloakofthefallingstars.html>Cloak of Falling Stars</a></b>, Gathu troll on the <b><a href=http://mmo.gameznet.com/eq/new/equipment/lazy/ironscrollofwar.shtml>Iron Scroll of War</a></b> and our bank on the <b><a href=http://mmo.gameznet.com/eq/new/equipment/lazy/reaver.shtml>Reaver</a></b><br><br>Was another fun day, will see what happens tomorrow...  <br>On the plus side Kellen has added a wee cgi that lets me put files straight on our server, so I can post screenshots (yaay) <img src=/news/icon/icon7.gif> <br><center><br><a href="/news/sontdead.jpg" target=new border=0><img src="/news/sontdeadTHUMB.jpg" border=0></a> <a href="/news/statue.jpg" target=new border=0><img src="/news/statueTHUMB.jpg" border=0></a> <a href="/news/statuedead.jpg" target=new border=0><img src="/news/statuedeadTHUMB.jpg" border=0></a></FONT></TD></TR><BR><BR></TABLE>
