dropped the crappy SK sword - which no one wanted so Aerylin promptly looted and killed himself with.<br><br>Grats to all involved and was alot of fun!<br><br><center><a href="/news/yelinak1-dead.jpg" target=new border=0><img src="/news/tn_yelinak1-dead.jpg" border=0></a></center></FONT></TD></TR><BR><BR></TABLE>
