eux</b> received.  Went to Skyfire afterwards for another meeting with Talendor.  Congrats to Seleron-DK for the RBB, Frakis for the pouch, <b>Belain</b> for the Dragon Hero bracer.  The red scale was given to Kaas-DK and the bard horn to someone. ;)   The Vindicator attempt was again postponed due to lack of people, maybe some day we'll have enough interested folks online at the same time to get our 2nd victory over him. ;)</FONT></TD></TR><BR><BR></TABLE>
