<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 WIDTH=640 NOF=LY><TR VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><TD WIDTH=640><b><CENTER><FONT COLOR="#66FFCC" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica">Veeshan's Peak!</FONT></b><FONT SIZE="-2" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica"><br>Sunday, May 20, 2001 by <a href="mailto:kellen@shardsofavalon.com">Kellen</a></FONT><br><br></CENTER><FONT SIZE="-1" FACE="Tahoma,Verdana,Arial,Helvetica"><CENTER><b>Silverwing Slain, Hoshkar Victorious</b></CENTER><br>Our last several Trakanon raids had garnered us enough keys to start a decent attempt at Veeshan's Peak, one of the zones we have yet to visit, until last night...<br><br>We set out with the mission of killing Silverwing while learning as much as we can about the zone, and also possibly make an attempt at Hoshkar.  It was a bit anti-climactic however as Silverwing fell down faster than Calek does when he plays with the cocks in Dreadlands. <br><br>As expected, Hoshkar proved to be a tougher challenge, winning both fights against us.  The first fight was sketchy though as we got a guardian wurm roamer that aggro'ed during the fight and by our luck it was the one that fears and dispells =P   We still lost our rematch however so it's Hoshkar 2 - Us 0 (for now).... but we'll be back for sure. ;)<br><br><center><a href="/news/silverwing1.jpg" target=new border=0><img src="/news/tn_silverwing1.jpg" border=0></a> <a href="/news/hoshkar1.jpg" target=new border=0><img src="/news/tn_hoshkar1.jpg" border=0></a></center><br><br>We got a few nice items from Silverwing also, albeit more of just "trophies" nowadays. Congrats to the winners:  Eevia-DK and Raethen-VS for <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/data/item.asp?Id=2932">Robes of Smothering</a>, <b>Ceinwen</b> for <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ss/dragon_spine_staff.jpg">Dragon Spine Staff</a>, and Lesbrina-DK for the <a href="http://www.gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ss/hammerofthedragonborn.jpg">Hammer of the Dragonborn</a> (nice right-click buff!)<br><br><br><center><b>WIZARD EPIC QUEST COMPLETED</b><br>As a prelude to our Veeshan's Peak raid, Venril Sathir showed up so a quick raid produced a gnarled staff and Elder Spiritist Leggings (Congrats to Damas-DK).   The staff went to Nadil thus completing his <a href="http://www.gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ss/staffofthefour.jpg">Staff of the Four</a>.<br>WTG and congratulations!<br><br><img src="/news/nadil-epic.jpg"></center></FONT></TD></TR><BR><BR></TABLE>
