rgot to list down)<br><br>Congratulations to Ming (VS) for the shield,  Skeep (DK) for the orb, <b>Kellen</b> for the horn, and Calren (DK) for the scales.<br><br><center><b>RETURN TO WESTERN WASTES</b></center><br>SoA/DK went back to Western Wastes last Friday for some more dragon-slaying fun.  The activity was marred once again by that dragon bitch Cargalia (her days are numbered I tell ya) when she roamed by our staging spot and caused some delays due to CR but once we were able to set up, it was a steady stream of dead dragons and good loot.   We got a bunch of NoS-type talismans (5ac +4 to all stats/resists), some Peerless/Reinforced dragon armor and a bunch of spells.  Congrats to all winners!<br><br><CENTER><A HREF="/news/esorpa.jpg" target=new border=0><IMG SRC="/news/tn_esorpa.jpg" BORDER=0></A><br>Esorpa of the Ring <br>(one of the few dragons in Western Wastes that casts SILENCE)</CENTER><br><br><br><center><b>NEW HIGH PRIEST</b><br><br>Congratulations to <b>Borniel</b> for achieving the level 60 milestone this weekend<br><br><IMG SRC="/news/level60.jpg" BORDER=0><br></center><br><br></FONT></TD></TR><BR><BR></TABLE>
